text: Célia Allamargot () also known as Célia Pashley (born 14 April 1986) is a former professional French female squash player. == Squash career== She competed in the Women's World Team Squash Championships in 2004, 2006 and 2008. Célia Allamargot achieved her highest singles career ranking of 61 in June 2009. == References == Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:French female squash players Category:Sportspeople from La Rochelle
